name: Criarcy's Fantasy to Experience
description:
Original v1.0 Checkpoint merged between Darelites Fantasy-Leaning-To-Anime mix and Experience 7.0

Note: v2.0 and beyond has additional sources - see below for breakdown

This model has vae baked in - combination of at least 3 at this point (I've lost track)

The full versions are available along side a safetensors and ckpt pruned version for each iteration!

This model has proved to be extremely versatile. Extremely good at all kinds of nsfw, but has proven to provide amazing results across many genres and styles - see the sample images for examples; prompts included!

Version Breakdowns:

v1.1 has the Delicate Colors vae baked in (please note all further versions have it baked in as well

v2.0 has a slight stylistic update, with the major change being the addition of both MeinaMix as well as DigitalSoul

v3.0 has another slight stylistic change for altered proportions; the addition of Sardonyx Blend

Give this a rate and show me your generations if you'd be so kind!
